    <item>
      <title>加拿大释放公共土地解决住房短缺问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/canada-frees-up-public-lands-to-tackle-housing-shortage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多领导的政府确定了 56 处联邦地产，面积相当于约 2,000 个冰球场，可在这些地产上建造数百套新的经济适用房，以应对可用土地稀缺导致的住房短缺问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/canada-frees-up-public-lands-to-tackle-housing-shortage</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 17:04:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔的立场转变令交易员们争论降息规模和路径</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/powell-s-pivot-leaves-traders-debating-size-path-of-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[既然美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔已经明确表示下个月将降息，债券交易员正重点关注首次降息的规模以及未来的宽松路径。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/powell-s-pivot-leaves-traders-debating-size-path-of-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 16:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>科威特内阁改组，财政部长换届</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/kuwait-replaces-finance-minister-as-part-of-cabinet-reshuffle</link>
      <description><![CDATA[科威特统治者周日签署法令，改组海湾国家内阁，包括罢免财政部长和更换其他三名部长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/kuwait-replaces-finance-minister-as-part-of-cabinet-reshuffle</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 15:22:32 GMT</pubDate>
